Welcome to the exercises related to [[Modern Greek/Lesson 8x|Lesson 1]].

Click "▼" to check your answers.

== Hello! ==
How would you respond to:
{{Question-answer
| question = Γεια σου!
| answer = Γεια σου!
}}
{{Question-answer
| question = Πώς είσαι;
| answer = Καλά!
}}
{{Question-answer
| question = How would you greet someone in the morning?
| answer = Καλημέρα
}}

== How are you? ==
Arrange the following in best to worst.
{{Question-answer
| question = Εντάξει, Έτσι κι έτσι, Αρκετά καλά, πολύ καλά!
| answer = πολύ καλά, Αρκετά καλά, Εντάξει, Έτσι κι έτσι
}}

== Greetings ==
Translate the following Greek sentences into English:
{{Question-answer
| question = Ναι, είμαι καλά, εσύ;
| answer = Yes, I'm well and you?
}}
{{Question-answer
| question = Καληνύχτα! 
| answer = Goodnight!
}}
{{Question-answer
| question = Πώς είστε;
| answer = How are you (plural)?
}}
{{Question-answer
| question = Γεια σου!
| answer = Hello! 
}}


Translate the following English sentences into Greek:
{{Question-answer
| question = Good evening!
| answer = Καλησπέρα!
}}
{{Question-answer
| question = Goodbye!
| answer = Αντίο!
}}
{{Question-answer
| question = Thank you!
| answer = Ευχαριστώ
}}
{{Question-answer
| question = I am ok.
| answer = Είμαι εντάξει.
}}

== Dialogue ==
Try translating the following dialogue:
{{Question-answer
| question = Αντώνης: Γεια σου!
| answer = '''''Anthony''': Hello!''
}}
{{Question-answer
| question = Ανθή: Γεια σου!
| answer = '''''Anthi''': . Hello!''
}}
{{Question-answer
| question = Αντώνης: Πώς είσαι;
| answer = '''''Anthony''': How are you?''
}}
{{Question-answer
| question = Ανθή: Καλά είμαι! Εσύ πώς είσαι;
| answer = '''''Anthi''': I'm well! You how are you?''
}}
{{Question-answer
| question = Αντώνης: Καλά.
| answer = '''''Anthony''': Well.''
}}
{{Question-answer
| question = Ανθή: Γεια σου!
| answer = '''''Anthi''': Goodbye!''
}}
{{Question-answer
| question = Αντώνης Γεια σου! 
| answer = '''''Anthony''': Goodbye!''
}}

