{{Reading level|Intermediate}}

This is a pre-algebra text for adult students at a two-year college. This text is meant to facilitate teaching via the Socratic method. The book also endeavors to connect topics through themes that are useful to adults, as opposed to covering fractions, decimals, and percentages in three separate chapters, as if they were unconnected concepts.

