Welcome to the exercises related to [[Zulu/Lesson 4|Lesson 4]].

Click "▼" to check your answers.

== How long have you been working for? ==
How would you respond to: (Assume for these questions that your name is Lebohang Ndlovu and that you're a student in Pretoria in your 3rd year. But you come from Johannesburg. You are 22 years old. Your mother is a cook. Your brother is teacher. You have two friends called Sipho and Mfanafuthi. Sipho stays in Cape Town.)
{{Question-answer
| question = Igama lakho ngubani?
| answer = Igama lami nguLebohang.
}}
{{Question-answer
| question = Laba ngobani?
| answer = Laba abangane bami nguSipho nonguMfanafuthi.
}}
{{Question-answer
| question = Wena uphumaphi?
| answer = (Mina) ngiphuma eGoli.
}}
{{Question-answer
| question = uSipho uhlala kuphi?
| answer = uSipho uhlala eKapa.
}}



== Do you know... ==
Translate the following Zulu sentences into English:
{{Question-answer
| question = Uyamazi uNelson wakwaMandela?
| answer = Yebo, ngiyamazi. noma(or) Cha angimazi.
}}

Translate the following English sentences into Zulu:
{{Question-answer
| question = How long have you been working for?
| answer = (Wena) uneminyaka emingaki usenbenza?
}}
{{Question-answer
| question = My name is Simon Hlope.
| answer = NginguSimon wakwaHlope. 
}}
{{Question-answer
| question = The teacher is coming from school.
| answer = Uthisha uphuma esikoleni
}}
{{Question-answer
| question = We come from South Africa.
| answer =  (Thina) siphuma eNingizimu Afrika.
}}
{{Question-answer
| question = Where do you all stay?
| answer = (Nina) nihlalaphi/ nihlala kuphi?
}}
{{Question-answer
| question = I have studied for three years.
| answer = (Mina) ngineminyaka engu-3 ngifunda.
}}

Odd one out:
{{Question-answer
| question = Which one of the following is not a correct sentence: Uthisha uphuma esikoleni; Ngisebenzela eCrispy Chicken; Bona bahlala eNaturena; Yena uphuma eMelika.
| answer = Ngisebenzela eCrispy Chicken. (e cannot be used with sebenzela)
}}
{{Question-answer
| question = Which of these nouns is not a possible family member: umama; umkhulu; usisi; umkandi; ubhuti.
| answer = umkandi (repairman).
}}

== Dialogue ==
Try translating the following dialogue:
{{Question-answer
| question = '''''uSipho''': Sawubona Njabulo!''
| answer = '''''Sipho''': Hello Njabulo!''
}}
{{Question-answer
| question = '''''uNjabulo''':Yebo, sawubona Sipho. Unjani? ''
| answer = '''''Njabulo''':  Hello Sipho! How are you?''
}}
{{Question-answer
| question = '''''uSipho''': Ngiyaphila, Wena unjani?''
| answer = '''''Sipho''': I'm alive, how are you?''
}}
{{Question-answer
| question = '''''uNjabulo''': Nami ngisaphila.''
| answer = '''''Njabulo''': I'm still alive. 
}}
{{Question-answer
| question = '''''uSipho''': Uneminyaka emingaki ubudala?''
| answer = '''''Sipho''': How old are you? ''
}}
{{Question-answer
| question = '''''uNjabulo''': Ngineminyaka engu-48. Uneminyaka engu-17?''
| answer = '''''Njabulo''': I am thirty two. Are you seventeen?''
}}
{{Question-answer
| question = '''''uSipho''': Cha, Ngineminyaka engu-16 ubudala!''
| answer = '''''Sipho''': No, I am sixteen years old!''
}}
{{Question-answer
| question = '''''uNjabulo''': Ubaba wakho usebenza kuphi?''
| answer = '''''Njabulo''': Where does your father work?''
}}
{{Question-answer
| question = '''''uSipho''': Yena usenbenza eFNB. Usenbenzaphi?''
| answer = '''''Sipho''': He works at FNB. Where do you work?''
}}
{{Question-answer
| question = '''''uNjabulo''': Ngisebenza eNaturena kodwa ngiphuma eThekwini. Ufundaphi?''
| answer = '''''Njabulo''': I work in Naturena but I'm from Durban. Where do you study? ''
}}
{{Question-answer
| question = '''''uSipho''': Ngifunda eParktown Boys.''
| answer = '''''Sipho''': I learn at Parktown Boys.''
}}
{{Question-answer
| question = '''''uNjabulo''': Umama wakho uyasebenza na?''
| answer = '''''Njabulo''': Does your mother work?'' 
}}
{{Question-answer
| question = '''''uSipho''': Yebo, yena ungunesi.''
| answer = '''''Sipho''': Yes, she's a nurse.''
}}
{{Question-answer
| question = '''''uNjabulo''': Sala kahle!''
| answer = '''''Njabulo''': Stay well (Goodbye)''
}}
{{Question-answer
| question = '''''uSipho''': Hamba kahle!''
| answer = '''''Sipho''': Go well (Goodbye)!''
}}

