== Overview ==
'''''Tebos''''' are ash-coloured warthogs with the ability to become invisible, making them extremely dangerous creatures.
== Extended Description ==
{{Muggles' Guide to Harry Potter/Beginner Spoiler}}
Tebos are found in Congo and Zaire. Their hide is valuable in the making of protective shields and clothing.
