== Used in constructors? ==

Is '''super''' also used in constructors?

<pre>
public class MyClass2 extends MyClass1 
{
  ...
  // constructor
  public MyClass2(ClassA1 arg1, ClassA2 arg2, ClassA3 arg3)
  {
    super(arg1, arg2) // calls MyClass1 constructor
    ...
  }
}
</pre>. [[User:Albmont|Albmont]] ([[User talk:Albmont|talk]]) 19:21, 30 December 2009 (UTC)
:Yes, as you write it. 20:12, 29 November 2013 (UTC)

